  "page": "Riverman (tavern)",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><div role=\"note\" class=\"hatnote navigation-not-searchable\" style=\"font-style: italic;padding-left: 1.6em;margin-bottom: 0.5em;\">For inhabitants of the riverlands, see <a href=\"/index.php/Rivermen\" title=\"Rivermen\">Rivermen</a>.</div>\n<p>The <b>Riverman</b> is a tavern in <a href=\"/index.php/Selhorys\" title=\"Selhorys\">Selhorys</a> that <a href=\"/index.php/Qavo_Nogarys\" title=\"Qavo Nogarys\">Qavo Nogarys</a> is known to frequent.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Recent_Events\">Recent Events</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Riverman_(tavern)&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Recent Events\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Dance_with_Dragons\"><i>A Dance with Dragons</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Riverman_(tavern)&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Dance with Dragons\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p><a href=\"/index.php/Jon_Connington\" title=\"Jon Connington\">Griff</a> tells <a href=\"/index.php/Haldon\" title=\"Haldon\">Haldon</a> to look for <a href=\"/index.php/Qavo_Nogarys\" title=\"Qavo Nogarys\">Qavo Nogarys</a> at the Riverman, the <a href=\"/index.php/Painted_Turtle\" title=\"Painted Turtle\">Painted Turtle</a>, and his other places.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd22.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd22.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\">